        <p class="file-label text-lg text-zinc-400 text-center">Drag and drop your excel file here or <span class="text-blue-600">browse</span></p>
      </label>
      <input type="file" name="productFile" id="productFile" class="hidden" accept=".xlsx, .xls">
      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn px-[24px] py-[12px] rounded-[58px] w-max mx-auto cursor-not-allowed bg-blue-600 text-white" disabled>Upload</button>

      <ul class="list-disc ml-[20px]">
        <li>Excel file must have columns name, description, price, category, subcategory, stock and brand</li>
        <li>To create points in description seperate the description with semicolon ";" .</li>
        <li>You can additionly add these columns if you want its not compulsary ( discountedPrice, trending, featured and published )</li>
      </ul>

